==Colonies & Outposts==
Due to the circumstances seen at this level, any tries to implement either a Colony or Outpost have been undone and it's currently infeasible.

==Entrances ==

* One has a chance to enter Level 448 when they hide from entities on any level. The chance of getting noclipped to Level 448 increases by 5% every minute they are in their hiding spot.

* Entering a peculiar room on [[Level 447]] will lead to this level.

*Breaking a radio on [[Level 26]] will send one here.

==Exits ==

* One can usually exit Level 448 if they jump out of a window showing [[Level 55]]’s hills. This will take them to that exact level.

